1.0     SUMMARY OF CHANGES



COBOL VERSION 6A(332) REPLACES ALL PREVIOUS  VERSIONS  OF  COBOL.
INCLUDED  IN  VERSION 6A ARE NUMEROUS BUG FIXES AND A PRELIMINARY
OVERLAY CAPABILITY.  SEE MINOR ENHANCEMENTS BELOW.

COBOL VERSION 6(222) PROVIDES SEVERAL NEW FACILITIES  WHICH  WERE
NOT   INCLUDED  IN  ANY  PREVIOUS  COBOL  RELEASE.   THE  PRIMARY
ENHANCEMENTS ARE THE FOLLOWING:



          1 )  DATA BASE CAPABILITY


          2 )  COMMUNICATIONS FACILITY


          3 )  TEXT EDITING FACILITIES (STRING/UNSTRING)


          4 )  MINOR ENHANCEMENTS


          5 )  NUMEROUS BUG FIXES



EACH OF THESE CHANGES WILL BE BRIEFLY DISCUSSED BELOW.
